  "content": "<h2>关于我</h2>\n<h3>工作和学习</h3>\n<p>前端码工转全栈，正在学英语</p>\n<h3>娱乐</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>看动画电影</li>\n<li>读科幻小说</li>\n<li>玩游戏，塞尔达、哈迪斯、有氧拳击，想玩 FF7，没有机器，玩八方旅人卡关了;;</li>\n<li>运动，力训和骑行</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>联系我</h3>\n<p>在博客留言，或者通过邮件 <code>cyouike@duck.com</code> 联系我</p>\n<p>也可能在 Fediverse 偶遇</p>\n<h2>使用服务</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://gohugo.io/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Hugo</a>\n<span></span>\n: 世界上最快的静态网站生成器 (Golang)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/CaiJimmy/hugo-theme-stack\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Stack</a>\n<span></span>\n: 一款简洁的 Hugo 主题</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">GitHub</a>\n<span></span>\n: 博客源码托管和版本控制</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://cloudflare.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Cloudflare</a>\n<span></span>\n: 域名 DNS 解析、全球 CDN 加速</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://pages.cloudflare.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Cloudflare Pages</a>\n<span></span>\n: 博客自动集成部署和托管</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://twikoo.js.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Twikoo</a>\n<span></span>\n: 轻量、安全、易上手的评论系统</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://ibruce.info/2015/04/04/busuanzi/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">不蒜子</a>\n<span></span>\n：简洁的网页访问计数器</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>博客日志</h2>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div>2024-01</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<span>breakChange</span>\n</div>\n<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n<div>拆分博客</div>\n</a>\n<div>拆分成技术博客和私人博客</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div>\n<div>\n<div>2023-11</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<span>fix</span>\n</div>\n<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n<div>迁移服务</div>\n</a>\n<div>更换托管账号</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div>\n<div>\n<div>2023-05</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<span>domain</span>\n</div>\n<a href=\"https://ponder.lol\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n<div>更换域名为 ponder.lol</div>\n</a>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div>\n<div>\n<div>2022-12</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<span>theme</span>\n</div>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/CaiJimmy/hugo-theme-stack\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n<div>使用主题 hugo-themes-stack</div>\n</a>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div>\n<div>\n<div>2022-10</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<span>domain</span>\n</div>\n<a href=\"https://anodicseal.xyz\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n<div>更换域名为 anodicseal.xyz</div>\n</a>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div>\n<div>\n<div>2022-09</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<span>domain</span>\n</div>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/monkeyWzr/hugo-theme-cactus\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n<div>使用 Cactus主题及同名评论系统 </div>\n</a>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
